{"tw": {"2492780": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "With Eyes Closed - Season 1", "steam_appid": 2492780, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "dlc": [3050840], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>With Eyes Closed</i></u><i>（第一季）</i>是一款成人視覺小說類型的驚悚遊戲。這款遊戲致力於帶來精彩的敘事、塑造鮮活的角色，同時也讓玩家控制故事的走向。此外，本遊戲內含大量火辣場景，與故事的發展緊密相關。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/918b3c6105d6077ef59a5dc84e5eea7f.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/918b3c6105d6077ef59a5dc84e5eea7f.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>劇情摘要</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你恢復意識時，發現自己在後車廂裡。你不記得自己是誰，不記得如何淪落至此。你的雙手被銬住了，附近還躺著兩具屍體。但你很快就會發現，更棘手的問題還在後頭。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/d7a8751bd212f1195f334e562314e86d.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/d7a8751bd212f1195f334e562314e86d.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能活著離開這裡嗎？你能找出綁架你的兇手並查明真相嗎？誰真正值得信任？誰只是為了一己私利在操弄你？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/e8aaf48488ed141df05ef81880b810b9.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/e8aaf48488ed141df05ef81880b810b9.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面對這些問題，你只能靠自己去尋找答案。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>分支故事線：</u>你的選擇將決定故事的走向。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.mp4?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>超高畫質的視覺效果：</u>本遊戲支援2K QHD解析度（選用）。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/91a372e2973fe8fb29e25de1694862c0.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/91a372e2973fe8fb29e25de1694862c0.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>極致流暢的動畫：</u>所有動畫都將以60 FPS呈現，同時支援2K QHD解析度（選用）。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/aec1bf7c195e32a3af50b50e4fe40103.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/aec1bf7c195e32a3af50b50e4fe40103.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>次世代角色模型：</u>所有主要角色都採用Genesis 9模型（2022年下半年推出）。Genesis 9帶來了雙倍的網格密度和8K的高清材質。這意味著，嘴部的紋理和形狀會更加精細，眼睛、睫毛和眉毛會更有質感，角色的姿勢會更自然（而非風格化），以及各種模型品質的提升！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/4c4d5cbb0367625d672bd26fff2b4acb.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/4c4d5cbb0367625d672bd26fff2b4acb.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要角色</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>凱特</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/3bc984222e7989984f3844ce807bd06a.avif?t=1775465554\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她是一位紅髮美人，值得信賴，總是樂於提供協助。你很難找到比她更棒的朋友了，尤其是考慮到她那傲人的魔鬼身材。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>伊娃</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/b9b28d67c2f3066e6b5d0a2683b00c61.avif?t=1775465554\" width=616 height=346 /></span>這位金髮醫生有著一雙湛藍的大眼睛。面對這位作風獨立的冰山美人，你能揭開她所隱藏的秘密嗎？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>露娜</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/ccb8e912187cce0129a4b16d1b677848.avif?t=1775465554\" width=616 height=346 /></span>她是一位落難的年輕女子，而你是唯一能幫助她的人。但她又將如何報答你呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>還有許多美女將會相繼登場！</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/a11f01751f2feb24579c4d3247070f23.avif?t=1775465554\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過7萬詞的英文文本量。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過3000張靜態圖片。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過100個動畫。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲時長約為4到7個小時。</p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>With Eyes Closed</i></u><i>（第一季）</i>是一款成人視覺小說類型的驚悚遊戲。這款遊戲致力於帶來精彩的敘事、塑造鮮活的角色，同時也讓玩家控制故事的走向。此外，本遊戲內含大量火辣場景，與故事的發展緊密相關。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/918b3c6105d6077ef59a5dc84e5eea7f.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/918b3c6105d6077ef59a5dc84e5eea7f.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>劇情摘要</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你恢復意識時，發現自己在後車廂裡。你不記得自己是誰，不記得如何淪落至此。你的雙手被銬住了，附近還躺著兩具屍體。但你很快就會發現，更棘手的問題還在後頭。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/d7a8751bd212f1195f334e562314e86d.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/d7a8751bd212f1195f334e56231