 Closed - Season 1", "steam_appid": 2492780, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "dlc": [3050840], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>With Eyes Closed</i></u><i> - Season 1</i> is a thriller in the adult visual novel genre. It concentrates on storytelling, realistic characters, and letting players control the development of the story. The game also features plenty of hot scenes that are interwoven into the storyline. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/918b3c6105d6077ef59a5dc84e5eea7f.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/918b3c6105d6077ef59a5dc84e5eea7f.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STORY</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You came to consciousness in the trunk of a car. You don't remember who you are and how you got there. Your hands are cuffed, and two dead bodies are lying around. But very soon you will learn that this is not the biggest of your problems. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/d7a8751bd212f1195f334e562314e86d.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/d7a8751bd212f1195f334e562314e86d.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you make it out alive? Will you find out who kidnapped you and why? Will you learn whom you can really trust and who is just using you for their own purposes? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/e8aaf48488ed141df05ef81880b810b9.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/e8aaf48488ed141df05ef81880b810b9.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The answers to these questions depend only on you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Branching storyline.</u> Your decisions determine how the story is told.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.mp4?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Ultra quality visuals.</u> The game is available in 2k QHD resolution (optional). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/91a372e2973fe8fb29e25de1694862c0.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/91a372e2973fe8fb29e25de1694862c0.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Extremely smooth animations.</u> All animations are done in 60 fps and are also available in 2k QHD (optional). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/aec1bf7c195e32a3af50b50e4fe40103.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/aec1bf7c195e32a3af50b50e4fe40103.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Next gen character models.</u> All main characters use Genesis 9 model, which was released in late 2022. Genesis 9 brings double the mesh density and 8K HD materials. This means more detailed mouth textures and shapes, higher quality eyes, eyelashes, and eyebrows, less stylized/more natural postures and so much more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/4c4d5cbb0367625d672bd26fff2b4acb.poster.avif?t=1775465554\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/4c4d5cbb0367625d672bd26fff2b4acb.webm?t=1775465554\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MAIN CHARACTERS</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kate</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/3bc984222e7989984f3844ce807bd06a.avif?t=1775465554\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A redheaded beauty, trustworthy, and always ready to help. You could hardly wish for a better friend, especially one with such curves. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eva</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/b9b28d67c2f3066e6b5d0a2683b00c61.avif?t=1775465554\" width=616 height=346 /></span>Blonde doctor with big blue eyes. Can you find out what lies behind the mask of a self-sufficient and icy woman? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Luna</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/ccb8e912187cce0129a4b16d1b677848.avif?t=1775465554\" width=616 height=346 /></span>A young lady in distress, and you're the only one who can come to her aid. But how will she reward you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>And many other girls are waiting for you!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492780/extras/a11f01751f2feb24579c4d3247070f23.avif?t=1775465554\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 70000 words.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 3000 static pictures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 100 animations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4-7 hours of gameplay.</p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>With Eyes Closed</i></u><i> - Season 1</i> is a thriller in the adult visual novel genre. It concentrates on storytelling, realistic characters, and letting players control the development of the story. The game also